text: provide function retrieve multi-dimensional data including genomic, epigenomic, transcriptomic, proteomic data TCGA (note, actually contains data TCGA/TARGET/GTEx databases) CCLE Pan-Cancer dataset single identifier (e.g., gene, protein). Check parameters: TCGA gene expression data, use Xena dataset ID TcgaTargetGtex_rsem_gene_tpm includes 19131 samples tumor tissue samples normal tissue samples. expression value unit log2(tpm+0.001). Let’s check several examples.
